{"tid":2349053,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"共產黨：三峽發電量創世界記錄 澳洲煤?狗也不屌","createTime":"2021-01-01T08:47:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-01T16:40:13.000Z","uid":21470,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"4b3c9a5bd7f385cc47c95b0151c58fe08df0bf47","tid":2349053,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T08:47:26.000Z","msg":"三峽水電站去年生產清潔電能創世界記錄<br />\n<br />\n全球最大的長江三峽水電站，去年全年累計生產清潔電能1118億千瓦時 ，刷新世界記錄，比南美伊泰普水電站在16年創下的舊發電記錄，多出87億千瓦時，相當於可供上海去年用電約8個月，減少二氧化碳排放超過9400萬噸、二氧化硫2.2萬噸、氮氧化物2.1萬噸。<br />\n<br />\n國家主席習近平在聯合國大會出，中國會力爭在2030年前實現二氧化碳排放達峰值，2060年前實現碳中和。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/china/2373063\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Fchina%2F2373063&d=3ylU62tgaeYkhBfBjxJ1gdAAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=4d965471\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/china/2373063</a>"},{"pid":"41823353e75df0e0c3ad26b4364ed7c0d4995b5c","tid":2349053,"uid":51271,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T08:48:08.000Z","msg":"因為五六月果時落雨落到就快沖爛你個壩"},{"pid":"b911c1bce23a9f4d5aea3618f0b38890ef39fe4d","tid":2349053,"uid":4574,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"41823353e75df0e0c3ad26b4364ed7c0d4995b5c","tid":2349053,"uid":51271,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T08:48:08.000Z","msg":"因為五六月果時落雨落到就快沖爛你個壩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T08:50:23.000Z","msg":"天災發電 <br />\n<br />\n厲害了 我的國"},{"pid":"5e577c85000e6ef9ae0ac4fee4ae414b4af00635","tid":2349053,"uid":321002,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T13:13:56.000Z","msg":"凍死多啲人，咪可以環保啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e43bf335ccb23730547b1de36a8b55a2153dc315","tid":23490